          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## MARDOT I-85 corridor \u2014 camera + lidar fused, station by station.\n\nThe ten perception stations strung along I-85 through metro Atlanta (Gwinnett \u2192 downtown \u2192 Newnan). Each cabinet runs two cameras and a lidar; their per-zone counts are reconciled into a single fusion agreement ratio and class mix. The map and station strip show the whole corridor at a glance; the fusion, queue, incident, and per-lane panels below drill into the stations you pick. All SAE J2735-style perception events, vendor-neutral, joined only after they land in ClickHouse."
      }
    },
