      "description": "lidar zone count vs. average per-camera lane volume (camera total \u00f7 distinct camera device count) over the dashboard time range \u2014 normalizes for 2 cameras vs. 1 lidar per cabinet so both modalities measure comparable per-sensor volume. Green band 0.7\u20131.3 is expected sensor agreement; amber is borderline; red is disagreement.",
